{"tid":584743,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連登皇馬褂苦主 — 癲狗廚子","createTime":"2018-03-08T05:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T14:39:53.000Z","uid":48796,"like":89,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8916725ad85f9c71f9896d3cc0912f3c3a0ba39e","tid":584743,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:05:34.000Z","msg":"話說admin登詔書公佈佢處死咗個NNYY<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/584268/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/584268/page/1</a><br />\n順便解釋點解ban佢唔ban「肥絲大隻」<br />\n<br />\n點知個矛頭去晒肥絲度，民怨沸騰<br />\n又變成討論肥絲行為有冇問題<br />\n甚至懷疑肥絲同admin有親，有皇馬褂著<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>喺度我想講下長期被肥絲滋擾嘅苦主 &mdash; 癲狗廚子</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n逢親會員「癲狗廚子」開post<br />\n肥絲就會撲入嚟貼啲水蛇春咁長嘅圖文滋擾佢：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/580185/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/580185/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/579207/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/579207/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/579171/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/579171/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/578699/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/578699/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/573398/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/573398/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/572399/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/572399/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/571000/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/571000/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/570857/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/570857/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/568897/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/568897/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/568880/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/568880/page/1</a><br />\n重有好多，九成都係，唔撚貼了，自己睇：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/74981\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/74981</a><br />\n<br />\n呢啲唔叫「相同內容的回覆」?<br />\n唔叫「令主題難以閱讀」? <br />\n針對樓主同主題有冇關? <br />\n喂admin你ban得NNYY唔ban肥絲大隻?<br />\n<br />\n本來個post好哋哋，俾佢搞到唔想睇<br />\n就算鳩噏都應該受到保障<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">何況癲狗亦有好多認真分享飲食內容<br />\n係貢獻，係幫你提升緊論壇質素<br />\n質素呀！連登成日俾人詬病不及高登嗰啲呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n有貢獻嘅俾人搞你當睇唔到<br />\n破壞論壇嘅人你走去攬<br />\n成個壇就日撚日左左右右反肥絲撐肥絲<br />\n你想個壇發展成點撚樣?<br />\n喂你做下樣都好吖<br />\n樣都唔做不突止重幫佢死撐<br />\n你話佢冇皇馬褂我都唔撚信啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bd10cdbccba2ebe1eb6c7088b36127190095d2","tid":584743,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"好煩"},{"pid":"7251b9ea974fb7d2837279a148dd3ff227a2d474","tid":584743,"uid":21423,"like":10,"dislike":19,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:10:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b2d91c1dfe53a66a4bb9d059fca6524e0020d92","tid":584743,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fd105f8893ec76c73bd992e64b34610a942df2d","tid":584743,"uid":48796,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0b2d91c1dfe53a66a4bb9d059fca6524e0020d92","tid":584743,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"阻住我睇嘢呀, 兩個都BAN好未?<br />\n<br />\n重有, 未完㗎"},{"pid":"4782c0877408faf659c7d4111771d93c86a9dc81","tid":584743,"uid":48796,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>另一苦主 &mdash; 關羽雲長</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/32723\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/32723</a><br />\n<br />\n肥絲次次都入嚟貼關羽這一家圖文，水蛇春咁長<br />\n啲圖佢貼咗幾多次? 算唔算「相同內容的回覆」?<br />\n<br />\n人哋而家唔撚玩啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br